      "text": "Yeah, I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 93.5
    },
    {
      "end": 109.45999908447266,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 103.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 113.58000183105469,
      "text": "One last thought, one last life, one last moment to tell you",
      "start": 109.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 117.5,
      "text": "I'm never ever being here again",
      "start": 113.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 123.5,
      "text": "I'm down to this last thought of you and all I'll ever be",
      "start": 117.5
    },
    {
      "end": 129.9199981689453,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, oh, oh, now you hate me more",
      "start": 124.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 131.8800048828125,
      "text": "Is it gonna get worse?",
      "start": 129.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 137.16000366210938,
      "text": "So you try to ignore the things that got us here in the first place",
      "start": 131.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 141.97999572753906,
      "text": "And you look at me like a waste of space",
      "start": 137.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 147.9600067138672,
      "text": "I'm just wasting your space and time",
      "start": 143.60000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 155.36000061035156,
      "text": "All the packages and all the lines and everything I read to you to make you think you wanted me as yours",
      "start": 147.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 161.4600067138672,
      "text": "Well, guess what? I'm down, down, down, down to one last breath",
      "start": 155.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 170.16000366210938,
      "text": "One last breath, yeah, I'm just down, down, down, down to one last breath of you",
      "start": 161.52000427246094
    },
    {
      "end": 174.72000122070312,
      "text": "One last thought, I'm down, down, down, down to one",
      "start": 170.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 179.75999450683594,
      "text": "One single line on her as a year",
      "start": 174.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 186.16000366210938,
      "text": "I'll see you in your different perspective of life and death, reincarnation",
      "start": 179.75999450683594
    },
    {
